Package: broadbandmap.gov
Title: NTIA National Broadband Map API Client for R (Defunct)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the former NTIA National Broadband Map
    API at broadbandmap.gov. The API was decommissioned in December 2018. This
    package provides a catalog of the 29 original endpoints and status-checking
    utilities. The replacement FCC Broadband Map at broadbandmap.fcc.gov
    requires authentication.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: httr2, jsonlite, dplyr, tibble
